# myAlgo2 Core Rules

Read [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md) and [TASKS.md](../../TASKS.md) at session start.

## Architecture

- Strategy layer outputs `Signal` only — never call Futu API from `src/strategies/`
- Broker layer in `src/broker/` — no strategy logic
- Default trading env: **SIMULATE** with **`trading.paper_only: true`** (hard lock)
- **Never** run `run_live.py`, `--env real`, or set `paper_only: false` unless user explicitly says to switch to real trading
- Real trading (when unlocked) requires `--confirm` + user YES
- Account: **Futu HK** with `SecurityFirm.FUTUSECURITIES`

## After completing work

1. Run `make check`
2. Update [TASKS.md](../../TASKS.md) checkbox for the task ID
3. Do not commit secrets (`config/settings.yaml`, `.env`, passwords)

## Code style

- Python 3.10+, type hints where practical
- Match existing module layout; minimal diff
- New strategy = `.py` + `config/strategies/*.yaml` + registry entry + test
